---
title: Harissa Roast Chicken with Herbed Pumpkin-Chickpea Smash & Yoghurt
description: Biff! Bop! Blam! Hero Harissa to the rescue! We’ve dressed up simple chicken with a cape of this delicious paste – and what a superhero dinner it creates! Smashing chickpeas, conquering pumpkin, and backed up by its friends zesty lemon, herby parsley and cool yoghurt – you’ll be cheering for this scrumptious superstar all the way to the final bite.
